Package: antigravity-cli
Version: 1.1.3
Architecture: all
Maintainer: Alienkrishn [Anon4You]
Depends: curl, clang, python, glibc
Section: devel
Priority: optional
Homepage: https://antigravity.google/
Description: AI‑powered coding assistant (glibc wrapper for Termux)
 Antigravity CLI provides real‑time code suggestions. This package
 downloads the official Linux ARM64 binary, applies necessary memory
 patches, and runs it inside the Termux glibc environment.
